verbose_text: Compared with the control samples, there were 1,384 DEGs identified in the mice with STZ induced diabetes with a fold change> = 2, including 85 DEGs with a Q-value < 0.05; 7 DEGs were identified in the healthy mice treated with Rosi with a fold change> = 2, with no DEGs with a Q-value < 0.05.
evidence: STZ-induced diabetes with a fold change >=2, including 85 DEGs
